### Get refresh token incidents from a timestamp.
# Description:
# - Retrieves incidents that occurred after the specified timestamp.
# - The 'from' parameter should be a SQL-compatible timestamp (e.g., 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS').
# - Requires ROLE_ADMIN.

GET http://localhost:8444/api/v1/table/tokens/incidents/refresh/from-timestamp?from=2024-01-01 00:00:00.000&limit=100
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/hal+json
